@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gsxykb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v0 / ((v0 + 0.06 + v2 + 0.86) / 0.99))
    tmp = wp.exp(tmp)
    tmp = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.04 * v1 + 0.08)) / 0.71)
    tmp = (wp.abs(0.66) - (tmp + wp.cos(v1 + 0.63)))
    v2 = 0.35
    tmp = wp.abs((v1 * tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
